{"id": "1403565579323047976", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "Gambling causes happiness", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:28:31.098000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565628731949147", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "That is why we exist:", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:28:42.878000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565642157789287", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "To gamble", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:28:46.079000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565726517690472", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "In essence, everything in life is essentially a gamble", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:29:06.192000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:31:49.211000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565788883058798", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "A conclusion with absolute results is only theoretical", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:29:21.061000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:32:06.262000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565841982685185", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "Why? Because outside variables exist", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:29:33.721000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403565981472657418", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "And these “outside variables” are limitless", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:30:06.978000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403566029317079092", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "The chances of things going wrong will never be 0", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:30:18.385000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403566169318883470", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "Thus, every decision, every second we live, every second we think and breath and eat, is, in essence, a gamble", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:30:51.764000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403566322440212530", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "Therefore, I declare, with absolute certainty, that gambling is, quite literally, life", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:31:28.271000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403566832220373093", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "Only by knowing absolutely everything will you escape this fate", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:33:29.812000+00:00"}
{"id": "1403566959643332638", "channel_id": "1400750050208125010", "author_id": "1119757859807318046", "author_name": "lloyds_descendant", "content": "But, until then, the unknown will always affect the known", "timestamp": "2025-08-09T02:34:00.192000+00:00"}
